lead_paragraph: They came to see the Cleveland Indians clinch a World Series on Tuesday and when that did not happen, fans had to settle for a wave from Eddie Robinson, the last living member of the 1948-championship winning team.

headline.print_headline: Cleveland Settles for Wave From World Series Past
